description: Try our easy to follow Chicken Kebabs with Vegetable Stir-Fry recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Stir-fry,Quick & easy dinner,Low saturated fat,High fibre,High protein,Seafood free,Low sugar,Chicken,Asparagus,Dairy free
name: Chicken Kebabs with Vegetable StirFry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 bunch asparagus, trimmed, cut into 3cm pieces
1 large carrot, peeled, halved lengthways and thinly sliced
8 chicken kebabs (Honey Soy, Smokey Barbecue, Satay or Barbecue Plum)
440g thin egg noodles, cooked according to packet instructions (to serve)

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat grill on high. Place kebabs onto a baking tray. Cook under hot grill for 68 minutes, turning halfway.
Meanwhile, heat a wok over a high heat. Add oil and swirl to coat.
Add shallots and carrots and stirfry for 2 minutes. Add asparagus and corn. Stir fry for 1 minute. Add 1 tablespoon of water to wok and cover.
Cook for 2 minutes or until vegetables are just tender. Stir through cashew nuts. Serve vegetables with kebabs and noodles.
